verbose_text: A recent meta-analysis of this data showed that TRT improved fasting blood glucose by a mean of 0.48 mmol/L (P < 0.001), lowered triglyceride levels by a mean of 0.4 nmol/L (P < 0.001), and reduced waist circumference by approximately 4.1 cm (P = 0.03) in men with MetS.
evidence: reduced waist circumference by approximately 4.1 cm (P=0.03) in men with MetS
